{{template "header"}}
{{if .Regenerated}}
<p>Your token was regenerated. The previous token is revoked: sessions
still using it will stop at their next reconnect.</p>
{{else}}
<p>Your token is ready.</p>
{{end}}
<p class="warn">This is the only time it will be shown. Copy it now.</p>
<code class="token">{{.Token}}</code>
<p class="muted">Put it in <code>SHUCK_CHANNEL_TOKEN</code> (or
<code>~/.config/shuck/channel.json</code>) and restart your Claude Code
session.</p>
<p><a href="/">Back</a></p>
{{template "footer"}}
